dBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T15:02:25.000Z","msg":"建議你盡早睇醫生，到時病情更加嚴重會好難斷尾，就好似我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158c87d2979b7a0c67a0657b027224d3ba88d080","tid":461401,"uid":63576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T15:43:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我係愈大壓力果時愈enjoy <br />\n但控制唔太到自己<br />\n成日會無啦啦諗起d好笑野就大笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀緊書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n番緊工， 做幾份副工都好chur <br />\n同事覺得我好樂觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係好醜命生成，又時候嚴重上來，街上每一個人都好黑我憎，每見一樣野都唔合自己心意，我同你相反，所有野係我眼中都好負面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c67ee9d0084b44e8c4efc79f399c3233da8d066","tid":461401,"uid":63576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T15:44:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建議你盡早睇醫生，到時病情更加嚴重會好難斷尾，就好似我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心求教，係邊到求醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfb06c7166cfc48e75d9505cd75da7b06df3c37","tid":461401,"uid":63576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T15:47:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 一樣<br />\n成日覺得好壓抑<br />\n返工D人係咁追跟進追進度 <br />\n而家追到我都唔想理 樣樣outstanding<br />\n人又灰 樣樣野都無動力做<br />\n有時落樓返工行去搭車 行到一半已經發覺自己又諗緊D唔開心野 拿曬眉頭咁行路<br />\n呢種情況發生係放工果陣更甚<br />\n發覺果陣已經不斷同自己講唔好諗D唔開心野<br />\n但一放鬆返個人又會自動波諗返D唔開心野無限LOOP 好似無出路咁</blockquote><br />\n巴打做邊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係唔想處理果啲公事，但一念自己咁撚廢，就無曬動力做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10bf22b2a181dca25e159d7438e8da0d48f6b56","tid":461401,"uid":144198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T15:54:12.0